      <title>Thoma Bravo 突破僵局，在数天内向支持者返还数十亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/thoma-bravo-returns-billions-to-backers-in-days-defying-logjam</link>
